=== test.176: host resetintr read after post-fw msleep — stage=0 ===
Date: Mon Apr 20 18:18:37 BST 2026

Stage 0: skip_arm=1 — download_fw_nvram: enter_download_state (read-only) + BAR2 ioread32 probe + 442KB iowrite32 fw; sleeps 100 ms, reads host resetintr from fw->data, releases fw/NVRAM, returns -ENODEV.
(test.176: test.175 proved msleep(100) after the complete fw write survives. This run keeps that sleep, then reads resetintr from host firmware memory before release/return. Still no post-write ARM probe, device resetintr use, NVRAM write, readback, or ARM release.)

=== Pre-test BAR0 MMIO guard ===
BAR0 MMIO UR/I/O error (6ms) — device alive; SBR in probe should fix. Proceeding.

